Basic Building Blocks
1)Module -To import 3rd party Modules (root module -app.module.ts)
2)component -To create html,css, and its files

Basic commands
1)To create new project        -ng new projectname
2)To create new component_name  -ng g c name
3)To run angular files          - ng serve --open


Basic Concept
Data binding (share data betwen components)
ts->component
thml->view

1)One Way Data binding
Data sharing only one direction(ts->html or html->ts)
   1.1)component to view (ts-> html file)
       a)String interpolation -{{expression}}
       b)property binding -[attribute_name]="property"

    1.2)View to components(html to ts)
         a)Event binding -(event_name)="function_name()"
         b)Event binding using $event -(event_name)="function_name($event)"
         c)Event binding using template referencing variable - #variable_bame
2)Two Way Data binding(Data sharing in both direction)
       i)ngModel binding - import formsModule in app.module.js
        syntax: [(ngModel)]="property_name"


Angular Routing 
to set a path for component
syntax:
        {
            path:value,component:component_name
        },
   login
   {
    path:'',component:SigninComponent
   }

